for 3 days. An alternative treatment is fenbendazole, another antiparasitic drug, with daily treatment required for 10-14 days.<br />\n<br />\nWhat is the success rate for treating?<br />\nMost infections will be cleared after the appropriate treatment."},{"pid":"27455ed738bf66abeb6661c2c3c10830ed8acf09","tid":2078422,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"想問下因咩事會帶貓貓去照xray ?"},{"pid":"4b5263ce91873c51676ce4fab97e35d6050858ed","tid":2078422,"uid":8780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27455ed738bf66abeb6661c2c3c10830ed8acf09","tid":2078422,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"想問下因咩事會帶貓貓去照xray ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"本身淨係諗住帶佢睇牙 佢之後幫我隻貓用聽筒聽佢話聽到我隻貓呼吸有問題 跟著就照xray 同驗埋血"},{"pid":"0405536cbf6fd17c7688df512d664bd1c2988b4d","tid":2078422,"uid":230251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:31:09.000Z","msg":"我隻貓b都照到肺白，係肺炎同支氣管炎，由於太細隻得400g，入咗三日氧氣箱，打咗三日藥，聽日開始可以留係屋企餵藥，希望快啲好返，睇咗成萬蚊醫生啦"},{"pid":"a983d08bcd2e83cc2c828d547d9c966193516651","tid":2078422,"uid":105888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"女朋友隻貓因為呼吸急促入咗院 試過上70幾<br />\n睇咗4間Total <br />\n做晒 X-ray 心電 ct<br />\n一個月後發現係腫瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 壓住個肺<br />\n一開頭以為心有事/肺炎/哮喘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知試極藥都無用<br />\n而家用類固醇暫時hold 到每分鐘25呼吸<br />\n又係就嚟三歲"},{"pid":"e8da28500c80d3faf3b6647e12676612088e8e8e","tid":2078422,"uid":8780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0405536cbf6fd17c7688df512d664bd1c2988b4d","tid":2078422,"uid":230251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:31:09.000Z","msg":"我隻貓b都照到肺白，係肺炎同支氣管炎，由於太細隻得400g，入咗三日氧氣箱，打咗三日藥，聽日開始可以留係屋企餵藥，希望快啲好返，睇咗成萬蚊醫生啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T1